---

## ‚ñ∂Ô∏è How to Run

1. Clone the repository:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/RenishSelaxteena/-Secure-Payment-Information-Manager
   ```

2. Install required packages:

   ```bash
   pip install flask
   ```

3. Run the Flask app:

   ```bash
   python app.py
   ```

4. Open your browser and go to:

   ```
   http://localhost:5000
   ```
5. To view the backend database :

Open DB Browser for SQLite.(app)
(download if you dont have)

Click on Open Database and select the payments.db file from the project folder.

Navigate to the Browse Data tab.

In the Table dropdown, select payment to view stored (encrypted) payment records.

